    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cosmetics applied to the lips that are composed of a fatty base containing waxes, oils, or emollients combined with color provided by pigments, often reds, or titanium dioxide for brightness and cover. Usually the material is formed into a stick, and is housed in a protective tube.</Note_Text>
